{"id":486696562,"lang":"java","time":"1 year, 3 months","timestamp":1619707057,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"2 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/486696562/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Ugly Number II","memory":"37.7 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int nthUglyNumber(int n) {\n        if(n==1) return 1;      //1 is 1st ugly number\n        \n        int arr[]=new int [n];\n        arr[0]=1;\n        \n        int p2=0;\n        int p3=0;\n        int p5=0;\n        \n        for(int i=1;i<n;i++){\n            arr[i]=Math.min(arr[p2]*2,Math.min(arr[p3]*3,arr[p5]*5));\n            \n            if(arr[i]==arr[p2]*2) p2++;\n            if(arr[i]==arr[p3]*3) p3++;\n            if(arr[i]==arr[p5]*5) p5++;\n        }\n        return arr[n-1];\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"ugly-number-ii"}
